post0.title: DynamoDB Quick Reference
post0.content: DynamoDB . Data Types . | Type | Symbol | Description | JSON Example | |—|—|—|—| | String | S | typical string | “S”: “this is a string” | | Number | N | Any int or float | “N”: “98”, “N”:”3.141592” | | Binary | B | Base64 encoded binary data | “B”: “nwaafrafs” | | Boolean | BOOL | true or false | “BOOL”: false | | Null | NULL | use for missing values | “NULL”: true | .
